# 🚀 Future Enhancements

- Complete `psx` implementation
- Recursive directory listing
- Recursive file copy
- Recursive file removal
- Colored terminal output
- Wildcard (`*`) support
- Symbolic link support
- Long listing format (`ls -l`)
