---

# 📈 Advantages

- Lightweight implementation
- Educational reimplementation of Unix commands
- Demonstrates direct kernel interaction
- Modular utility design
- Easy to understand and extend
- No external dependencies

---

# ⚠️ Limitations

- Linux-specific implementation
- Basic subset of standard Unix utility features
- Minimal command-line option support
- No recursive operations for file management
- `psx` is currently incomplete

